% =============================================================================
% Blog-level references — shared across all posts
%
% Usage: cite with [@key], @key, or [-@key] in your MDX/MD posts
%
% Priority: Per-post bib (src/content/blog/{slug}/references.bib) > 
%           Blog-level bib (this file) > 
%           Global bib (src/data/references.bib)
%
% A citekey defined in a per-post bib overrides the same key here.
%
% —————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————
%  SUBMODULE COMMIT WORKFLOW (manual)
%
%  src/content/blog is a git submodule pointing to wuyaxv/posts.git.
%  After editing this file, commit it to the submodule:
%
%    cd src/content/blog
%    git add references.bib
%    git commit -m "add/update blog-level references template"
%    git push
%
%  Then update the parent repo's submodule pointer:
%
%    cd /path/to/site
%    git add src/content/blog
%    git commit -m "update blog submodule"
%    git push
% =============================================================================
